d bei 8-10 °C getrunken. 750 ml', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '355-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-05-02 09:04:39', '2018-05-02 09:04:39', '', 355, 'http://luculos.com/?p=358', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
