(799, 1, '2019-01-28 14:23:36', '2019-01-28 14:23:36', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\">                             <img class=\"wp-image-340 alignnone\" src=\"https://luculos.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/vision.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"564\" height=\"261\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Lucullos, a politician and military of Roman ages and a deep taster, served his guests and friends the best of his </span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">time. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The historians refer to the notorious “Lucullian Meals”, </span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">where the quality, quantity and variety of flavors left </span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">everyone speechless.</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Having the same philosophy, we present Greek companies and their products, which are aimed at import, </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">distribution and sales companies, </span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">whose main goal is to offer the best to their customers as modern Lucullians.</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">If </span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">you believe that high quality, </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">special taste and the best prices are worth your own clientele, then you are at the</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">source! We have secured all of the above for each product presented and furthermore the cooperation with </span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">companies that have the same philosophy as ours and you!</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Enjoy a visual, informative journey into the range of products that tomorrow can belong to yours. We are at your </span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">disposal with the confidence of the best quality and the best prices. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">This is what we have secured for you from </span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">LUCULOS’s outstanding partners!</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Our Vision', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '36-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-01-28 14:23:36', '2019-01-28 14:23:36', '', 36, 'https://luculos.com/?p=799', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
